    <item>
        <title>Version 0.2.4</title>
        <pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 13:01:36 +0000</pubDate>
        <sparkle:version>6</sparkle:version>
        <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.2.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
        <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
        <link>https://github.com/birchsport/clipboard-manager/releases/tag/v0.2.4</link>
        <description><![CDATA[
<p>Multi-selection paste arrives, and this dialog finally shows what changed.</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Multi-paste</strong> — gather entries with <kbd>⇧Space</kbd> (or <kbd>⌘</kbd>-click), <kbd>⇧↑</kbd> / <kbd>⇧↓</kbd> to extend contiguously like Finder. <kbd>⏎</kbd> pastes them joined by a configurable delimiter (default newline). Configure in Settings → General → Multi-select.</li>
    <li><strong>Real release notes</strong> — Sparkle's "Update Available" dialog now shows what's actually in each release, derived from the commit log per version.</li>
</ul>
            <p style="font-size:smaller;color:#888;">Full notes: <a href="https://github.com/birchsport/clipboard-manager/releases/tag/v0.2.4">v0.2.4 on GitHub</a>.</p>
